menu "Clockwise Configuration"

  config HUB75_BLUE_GREEN_SWAP
    bool "Swap blue and green colors"
    help
        Some 64x64 HUB75 displays have the green and blue pins reversed. Enable this option to swap these pins.

  # All clockfaces are compiled in simultaneously.
  # Runtime selection is done via CWDriverRegistry (index 0-5).
  # The individual CONFIG_CLOCKFACE_* guards have been removed from each
  # cw-cf-0xNN CMakeLists.txt — all source files always compile.

endmenu
